Class Reservation

java.lang.Object
football.Reservation
public class Reservation
extends java.lang.Object

    • Reservation

      Reservation​(User bookedPlayer, Playground reservedPlayground, User playgroundOwner, double price, java.lang.String time)
      This is parameterize constructor for this class to set booked player, reserved playground, playground owner, price for reservation, and time. Creates reservation booked player, reserved playground, playground owner, price for reservation, and time of reservation.
      Parameters:
      bookedPlayer - This is player who booked playground.
      reservedPlayground - This is reserved playground.
      playgroundOwner - This is owner of reserved playground.
      price - This is the value of money which player will pay it for reservation.
      time - This is time of reservation.
